parameters:
Nobleman Crow: I am Crow, the master of this mansion. I
would like to request your help in solving the supernatural
phenomena occurring in the mansion.

Clea: May I ask for more details about the supernatural
phenomena?

Nobleman Crow: There have been damages to my research
facility, such as destruction and the release of animals.

Thief Nora: It might be the work of thieves! I think it
would be better to have the guards come and investigate!
Mage Relm: Is that what Nora-san says...

Priestess Sophia: Is there a reason why we can't call the
guards?

Nobleman Crow: I... don't want to say this, but I suspect
Kamari.

Nobleman Crow: I want to make it clear that I have complete
trust in her.

Priestess Sophia: However, it seems that Mr. Crow cannot
believe that it is not an inside job.

Nobleman Crow: There are no traces of the strong locks
being broken... I want to request Kamari's innocence to be
proven and the supernatural phenomena to be resolved!

Maid Kamari: Master, the preparation of the tea is
complete.
Nobleman Crow: Everyone, please take care of me!

Mage Relm: Understood. First, let me confirm whether magic
is the cause or not!
3.イベント後のプレイヤーの位置
Clea: I'm glad, it seems like you're not injured--

Mage Relm: Clea-san, you must not get closer! I didn't
sense this kind of magical power when I checked earlier...!

Clea: I don't fully understand, but do we have no choice
but to fight?

Clea: Then let's fight and investigate the phenomenon after
we knock them out.
Clea: So, was it Kamari-san who caused this after all?

Priestess Sophia: I wonder if the genius mage can solve the
reason why Kamari-san went berserk~?

Mage Relm: I have a hunch, but it seems that the magic
Crow-san was researching might be the cause.

Thief Nora: Didn't you say earlier that there was nothing
happening!?

Mage Relm: I think there was a problem with the content of
the command.
Mage Relm: Let's go talk to Crow-san.
3.イベント後のプレイヤーの位置
